column2:
"Welcome back, <%me>.
Did you help out those newbies like I
told you to?"

"Everyone starts at the bottom, and it's up
to experienced members like you to help
newbies in need. You got that?"

"...well, I think you're still a bit
sketchy when watching you though."

"Well, at least you came back in one piece,
<%me>. Thank goodness
for small miracles."

"<%me>！
お帰りなさい！
ちゃんと探索してきたのね？"

"誰でも未熟な時期ってのは
あるものなんだし、力のあるヤツが
きちんと先行してあげないとダメよ？"

"……まあ、あんたもまだまだ
見てて危なっかしいと思うけど。"

"ま、なにはともあれ無事でよかった！
これからもよろしくね！
<%me>！"
